<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Doctor Account Suspended - SID Clinic</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #334155;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grid" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" stroke-width="0.5"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grid)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 180px;
            height: 90px;
            border-radius: 5%;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 0 auto 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .logo img {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        
        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 45px 35px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 25px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);
        }
        
        .status-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }
        
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #475569;
        }
        
        .doctor-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .doctor-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
        }
        
        .doctor-card h3 {
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .doctor-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #235f8b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .doctor-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
        }
        
        .suspension-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.08);
        }
        
        .suspension-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
        }
        
        .suspension-card h3 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .suspend-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #dc2626;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        
        .icon-circle {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #235f8b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        
        .suspension-reason {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .suspension-reason h4 {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .warning-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .suspension-duration {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .suspension-duration h4 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .duration-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #dc2626;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.05);
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .steps-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #235f8b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .steps-list li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #235f8b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.4);
        }
        
        .button-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 35px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer h3 {
            color: #60a5fa;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #60a5fa;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #374151;
        }
        
        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .contact-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #60a5fa;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .disclaimer {
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid #374151;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
            
            .container {
                border-radius: 12px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 8px;
                padding: 12px 0;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .contact-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="https://sidclinic.com/logo.jpeg" alt="SID Clinic Logo">
            </div>
            <div class="header-content">
                <h1>Account Suspension Notice</h1>
                <p>Important information regarding your account status</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">
                <div class="status-icon">‚ö†</div>
                Account Suspended
            </div>
            
            <div class="greeting">Dear Dr. {{doctorName}},</div>
            
            <p class="intro-text">
                We regret to inform you that your SID Clinic account has been temporarily suspended. 
                This action has been taken after careful review of your account activity and compliance with our platform policies.
            </p>
            
            <div class="doctor-card">
                <h3>
                    <div class="doctor-icon">Dr</div>
                    Suspended Physician
                </h3>
                <div class="doctor-name">Dr. {{doctorName}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="suspension-card">
                <h3>
                    <div class="suspend-icon">‚ö†</div>
                    Suspension Details
                </h3>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <div class="icon-circle">üìÖ</div>
                        Suspension Date
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{suspensionDate}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <div class="icon-circle">üÜî</div>
                        Doctor ID
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{doctorId}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <div class="icon-circle">üè•</div>
                        Specialization
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{specialization}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if suspensionReason}}
            <div class="suspension-reason">
                <h4>
                    <div class="warning-icon">!</div>
                    Reason for Suspension
                </h4>
                <p style="color: #92400e; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">{{suspensionReason}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if suspensionDuration}}
            <div class="suspension-duration">
                <h4>
                    <div class="duration-icon">‚è∞</div>
                    Suspension Duration
                </h4>
                <p style="color: #dc2626; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">{{suspensionDuration}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>
                    <div class="steps-icon">‚Üí</div>
                    What This Means & Next Steps
                </h3>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        Your account is temporarily inactive and cannot accept new appointments
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        Review the suspension reason and address any concerns
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        Contact our support team for clarification or to appeal the decision
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        Take necessary actions to resolve the issues before suspension ends
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{supportUrl}}" class="cta-button">
                    <div class="button-icon">?</div>
                    Contact Support
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; font-style: italic;">
                We value your contribution to SID Clinic and are here to help you resolve any issues to restore your account access.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <h3>
                <div class="footer-icon">üè•</div>
                SID Clinic
            </h3>
            <p>Dedicated to providing exceptional healthcare services with integrity, professionalism, and patient-centered care.</p>
            
            <div class="contact-grid">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">@</div>
                    <span>Office@sidclinic.com</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">üìû</div>
                    <span>9274557987</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">üåê</div>
                    <span>www.sidclinic.com</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="disclaimer">
                This is an automated notification. Please do not reply directly to this email.
                For assistance, please contact us through our official channels listed above.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 